column5: I have an opportunity to go up with some guys and get an on ice bungalo this season. Wondering how this operation is and any comments from those that have been there.  http://www.chillywillys.ca/  Thanks!!  Burt
Went with them one year and would never go again.   Try Ice Bungalows...much better.
That seems to wrap that one up...
I'd try a different lake all together.
Which lake would you go too instead? thinking about going up there this winter
